* In modern notation:
  $$
    \begin{gathered}
      4 \times 4 + 3 \times 4 + 2 \times 4 + 1 \times 4 = 40; \\
      40 \times 40 = 1600;
      \quad 1600 \div 4 = 400.
    \end{gathered}
  $$
